Package <Unnamed>

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Hasher
    Interface for hashing functions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractHashtable
    Abstract class for hash table implementations utilizing different strategies.
    ChainHashtable
    Implementation of a hash table using collision chaining as its collision resolution strategy.
    DivisionHasher
    Hashing function utilizing character values.
    Djb2Hasher
    Hashing function utilizing the DJB2 algorithm.
    DoubleHashProbing
    Collision resolution strategy for open adressing.
    HashNode
    A node for the LinkedHashList class.
    LinearProbing
    Collision resolution strategy for open adressing, utilizes linear probing.
    LinkedHashList
    Implementation of a linked list to be used for a hash table that uses collision chaining as it's collision resolution technique.
    OpenHashtable
    Implementation of a hash table using forms of open adressing as it's collision resolution strategy.
    QuadraticProbing
    Collision resolution strategy for open adressing.
    Strategy
    Interface Strategy can be implemented for hashing strategies, has the method execute which executes the given strategy.
